{"tid":410840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙特教士稱女性只有半個腦 購物時只餘1/4 惹眾怒被禁從事宗教活動","createTime":"2017-09-23T09:47:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T13:40:29.000Z","uid":53379,"like":85,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"66026b021f070994b9314527dd2c1d0fc75e1fe9","tid":410840,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:47:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">沙特教士稱女性只有半個腦 購物時只餘1/4 惹眾怒被禁從事宗教活動</span></strong> <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170923/s00005/c0b8d8a2d9bba195ebf657762f6d154f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170923%2Fs00005%2Fc0b8d8a2d9bba195ebf657762f6d154f.jpg&h=ae104151&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n <br />\n沙特阿拉伯是全球唯一禁止女性駕駛的國家，近日當地一名教士稱女性的部只有男性的一半，去市場購物時更只剩下四分一，故應該被禁止駕車。他的言論引起很大反響，被指為侮辱女性，結果他被禁止從事宗教活動。 <br />\n <br />\n網上流傳的短片中，沙特阿拉伯教士艾爾赫傑里（Saad al-Hijri）發表有關「女士駕駛壞處」的演講，指女性只有男性腦袋的一半，而當她們去市場購物時更只剩下四分一個腦袋，因此不適合駕駛。 <br />\n <br />\n艾爾赫傑里發言的短片在社交媒體上引發怒火，許多推特用戶都分享有關片段，有網民認為艾爾赫傑里侮辱女性，指出女性生育並撫養男性，直指艾爾赫傑里應被禁止出席任何場合。亦有人貼出沙特阿拉伯的女科學家和學者照片，還擊艾爾赫傑里，倒過來質疑其智力。 <br />\n <br />\n片段上傳翌日，艾爾赫傑里被禁止從事宗教活動，他所屬的阿西爾省發言人稱，頒布禁令是因為艾爾赫傑里的言論貶低人類價值。 <br />\n <br />\n沙特阿拉伯是全球唯一禁止女性駕駛的國家，另外亦設有男性監護人制度，女性須得男性監護人同意才可出國旅遊、結婚和接受醫療服務等。 <br />\n <br />\n（英國廣播公司／每日郵報） <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170923/s00005/1506136224761\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170923%2Fs00005%2F1506136224761&d=fjFj6EJ132DHupDyyeTtecVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=1e83c479\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170923%2Fs00005%2F1506136224761&h=268df564\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170923/s00005/1506136224761</a>"},{"pid":"13edb6a652563e0a8fbcc69660b0b66912bf5e73","tid":410840,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:50:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ff32a285d22acf5091be5083dcd020b6283f99","tid":410840,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:50:37.000Z","msg":"說出了事㔤"},{"pid":"5981bcfeddaebe53d4da7ffe6a031fed1750fa2a","tid":410840,"uid":2984,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:52:34.000Z","msg":"批評佢果班人唔係死港女就不願面對現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad11c9773d2f53a803ba52354c418ad36d3f8df8","tid":410840,"uid":60115,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:54:38.000Z","msg":"講真話都唔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13a6412f2b1bab03ef5b6b39b113e4004a75ea5c","tid":410840,"uid":66759,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:58:12.000Z","msg":"唔好同女人講真話呢個道理都唔明"},{"pid":"8cc73204e3e29a5eed2d833264b489f0f6b81488","tid":410840,"uid":46151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T10:00:45.000Z","msg":"連登仔:佢可以做教主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a25be3ebcf304649f5b61cec84278d7db55793ba","tid":410840,"uid":49359,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T10:03:31.000Z","msg":"連登仔應該信蛔教瓦哈比教派"},{"pid":"56118bc1cc97ac3424fa2e4e9757ed90c7a13710","tid":410840,"uid":49197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T10:06:52.000Z","msg":"講真話D人又嬲嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d6c029d9c6563db3c49d554f2d5da06b1ae32bc","tid":410840,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T10:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15aeaaac2744431d50ff01f2712209113f1657cf","tid":410840,"uid":49197,"